{"model":"gpt-4.1-nano","messages":[{"role":"user","content":"Your job is to produce a final concise summary\nWe have provided an existing summary up to a certain point: \"Oliver, a curious mouse in an enchanted forest village, longs for adventure and new friends beyond his home. Setting out with cheese and a walking stick, he explores vibrant flora and listens to birds before reaching a sunlit clearing with a shimmering pond. There, he befriends Leo, a gentle lion who eagerly joins Oliver on his noble quest, promising a strong and everlasting friendship. With Leo by his side, their adventure expands to traversing meadows, climbing trees, crossing rivers, and meeting Freddie, a whimsical frog skilled in hopping and discovering hidden treasures.\"\nWe have the opportunity to refine the existing summary\n(only if needed) with some more context below.\n------------\n\"Freddie, with his emerald-green skin and mischievous grin, eagerly joined their quest. \"Ribbit! Oliver, my dear fellow, it seems that fate has brought us together. Allow me to lend my amphibious skills to our merry group. Together, we shall make quite the team!\"\n\nWith Oliver, Leo, and Freddie united, their bond grew stronger with each passing day. They shared laughter, sang songs, and told tales around the campfire. Oliver had finally found the true meaning of friendship, and his heart was filled with joy.\"\n------------\n\nGiven the new context, refine the original summary\nIf the context isn't useful, return the original summary.\n\nREFINED SUMMARY:"}]}HTTP/2.0 200 OK
